  "texts": [
    "Dialogflow allows for the expansion of Chatbot functionalities and the management of various aspects.",
    "In the specific case of F-One, we modified the Start Page in the Default Start Flow, through the Dialogflow CX console.",
    "The Start Page includes the Default Welcome Intent and it also includes handlers for the sys.no-match-default and sys.no-input-default events.",
    "The first one allows setting responses that the Chatbot will provide whenever the user's input does not match any intent within the handlers' scope.",
    "The second one allows setting responses that the Chatbot will provide whenever the user's input has not been received."
  ],
  "correct_citations": []
}